{"id":233008790,"title":"#分享 如何解決足底筋膜炎 (中文字幕)","content":"http://i.imgur.com/sPB5zJr.jpg\n\nhttp://bit.ly/2OihGab\n\n 這次的內容針對足底筋膜炎說明，很多人在面對這樣的狀況時，會嘗試按摩腳底，但這樣的方式只能讓症狀減緩，而不能根治問題，要解決問題之前要先知道問題所在，可以先檢查小腿是否有過度緊繃的問題，或是臀中肌肌力不足，以及胸椎是否無法充分伸展，導致旋轉角度有限，這些問題都有可能導致足底筋膜，或是身體其他關節或肌肉承受不必要的負荷而產生疼痛。 \n\n--\nFitting Room TW\n運動、健康相關資訊翻譯影片\n官方Blog\nhttp://fittingroomtw.blogspot.tw/\n官方臉書\nhttps://goo.gl/HZhAhS","excerpt":"這次的內容針對足底筋膜炎說明，很多人在面對這樣的狀況時，會嘗試按摩腳底，但這樣的方式只能讓症狀減緩，而不能根治問題，要解決問題之前要先知道問題所在，可以先檢查小腿是否有過度緊繃的問題，或是臀中肌肌力不","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"9b5213d6-4427-4a3c-b788-efa19493631c","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-02-03T11:57:06.125Z","updatedAt":"2020-02-03T11:57:06.125Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":5,"tags":[],"topics":["健身","足底筋膜炎"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"健身","forumAlias":"fitness","school":"FRTW","department":"fittingroomtw","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":true,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":4},{"id":"011ead16-9b83-4729-9fde-c588920c6c2d","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/sPB5zJr.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"93ec26be-3735-4abb-9097-bbc389f29b7d","url":"https://i.imgur.com/sPB5zJrl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/sPB5zJrl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/sPB5zJrl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-02-03T11:57:06.125Z","updatedAt":"2020-02-03T11:57:06.125Z"},{"id":"93ec26be-3735-4abb-9097-bbc389f29b7d","url":"http://i.imgur.com/sPB5zJr.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/sPB5zJr","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/sPB5zJrl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-02-03T11:57:06.125Z","updatedAt":"2020-02-03T11:57:06.125Z"}],"postAvatar":""}